Title: The ODE/IM correspondence and PT-symmetric quantum mechanics
Authors: Patrick Dorey, Clare Dunning and Roberto Tateo
Comments: 12 pages, 9 figures. Contribution to the proceedings of the NATO
  Advanced Research Workshop on Statistical Field Theories, Como, 18-23 June
  2001
Report-no: DCPT-02/01
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Mathematical Physics; Spectral Theory
\\
  A connection between integrable quantum field theory and the spectral theory
of ordinary differential equations is reviewed, with particular emphasis being
given to its relevance to certain problems in PT-symmetric quantum mechanics.
